{"tid":2364932,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Welcome to ICQ New","createTime":"2021-01-13T10:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T20:21:02.000Z","uid":49415,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5deb2158ad7f195e48a7a92025d8abba2ad299","tid":2364932,"uid":49415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"反樸歸真，用返ICQ<br />\nICQ是英語「I seek you」諧音，中文意思是：「我找你」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWikipedia: ICQ是最早出現的即時通訊軟件之一。ICQ源自以色列特拉維夫的Mirabilis公司（英語：Mirabilis (company)）（成立於1996年7月），由幾個以色列青年（包括Chan si hou Yair Goldfinger、Sefi Vigiser、Amnon Amir、Arik Vardi以及Arik之父親Yossi Vardi（希伯來語：יוסי ורדי））在1996年11月發明。<br />\n<br />\n2010年1月19日ICQ 7發佈。不過，官方版本不再支持繁體中文。在畫面上，排版更像MSN 8的設計，而且可以與Facebook等交友網站消息互通及匯入各電郵地址的通訊錄，所以較之前一直以來的版本更用戶化。4月28日，AOL將ICQ出售給俄羅斯的網絡公司Mail.Ru[2]，<br />\n<br />\n2011年11月15日新版ICQ官方免費iPhone及Android應用程式發佈。加入類似WhatsApp的用法及功能，啟動後就不用每次登入，長期在線，用法與流行的即時通訊軟件類似。由於ICQ突然發佈了手機程式，迅速引起了大量用家的注意，並有不少玩家重新開始使用ICQ。"},{"pid":"29c3f25a0f2926245c297df4f27ba88e6395d466","tid":2364932,"uid":30274,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3d52633247d5a20bb348f5d5d471b944ac3485","tid":2364932,"uid":49415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29c3f25a0f2926245c297df4f27ba88e6395d466","tid":2364932,"uid":30274,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp早前更新私隱政策，將帳戶內的電話號碼等資料與Facebook共享，引發用戶強烈不滿及反彈，同時令其他即時通訊軟件包括ICQ、Signal下載量急升。個人私隱專員今日(13日)亦指事件存在不少疑團，WhatsApp再就事件「補鑊」，重申WhatsApp和Facebook均無法取得用戶間的私人訊息，亦不會記錄任何人與他人間的信息或通話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2851768/【WhatsApp更新】Signal及ICQ下載增急增%E3%80%80WhatsApp再回應私隱專員質疑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2851768%2F%E3%80%90WhatsApp%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91Signal%E5%8F%8AICQ%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E5%A2%9E%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E%25E3%2580%2580WhatsApp%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e978ef55\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2851768/【WhatsApp更新】Signal及ICQ下載增急增%E3%80%80WhatsApp再回應私隱專員質疑</a>"},{"pid":"f775d0176330541b23a5e9c180f6571aa110b1cb","tid":2364932,"uid":49415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b3d52633247d5a20bb348f5d5d471b944ac3485","tid":2364932,"uid":49415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29c3f25a0f2926245c297df4f27ba88e6395d466","tid":2364932,"uid":30274,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp早前更新私隱政策，將帳戶內的電話號碼等資料與Facebook共享，引發用戶強烈不滿及反彈，同時令其他即時通訊軟件包括ICQ、Signal下載量急升。個人私隱專員今日(13日)亦指事件存在不少疑團，WhatsApp再就事件「補鑊」，重申WhatsApp和Facebook均無法取得用戶間的私人訊息，亦不會記錄任何人與他人間的信息或通話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2851768/【WhatsApp更新】Signal及ICQ下載增急增%E3%80%80WhatsApp再回應私隱專員質疑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2851768%2F%E3%80%90WhatsApp%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91Signal%E5%8F%8AICQ%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E5%A2%9E%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E%25E3%2580%2580WhatsApp%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e978ef55\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2851768/【WhatsApp更新】Signal及ICQ下載增急增%E3%80%80WhatsApp再回應私隱專員質疑</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"社交軟件轉會潮中，有人選擇從未使用過的新興平台如Signal、MeWe，也有人回到未有智能電話的年代，反璞歸真重裝早被遺忘的ICQ。有回歸ICQ的用家質疑，當大夥兒一窩蜂轉用Signal或MeWe時，究竟有否先了解相關軟件的背景？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/BNGBZ2ID5VALLIXKJFK3MFISDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FBNGBZ2ID5VALLIXKJFK3MFISDE%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=fe17b9a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FBNGBZ2ID5VALLIXKJFK3MFISDE%2F&h=df1e1b70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/BNGBZ2ID5VALLIXKJFK3MFISDE/</a>"},{"pid":"222e02eaa8d7c0cc8495eac41ceca3dcab1109d6","tid":2364932,"uid":40415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:21:02.000Z","msg":"禁煙禁得多食返鴉片"}]}